// User Config for vm-data — throwaway user for the multi data-pools ownership
// smoke test (pool-owners, ADR 0031).
//
// Merged on top of `.os/users/core/config.jsonc`. Unlike vm-test it ships NO
// secrets.json, so secrets_load is a no-op (the test has no age key source);
// no programs, to keep the install light and focused on data-pool ownership.

{
  "shell": "/bin/bash",
  "sudo":  true,
  "groups": [],
  "programs": [],
  "ssh_authorized_keys": []
}
